data.description: Introducing a rare gem, the first time on the market! Nestled in the coveted Highlands neighborhood, this expansive residence boasts over 3,300 sqft of luxury living with oversized bedrooms and bonus room. Park effortlessly in the large 3-car tandem garage. Step into the backyard oasis—picture perfect with a sprawling cement patio & fenced yard, providing ample space for gatherings and play. The heart of this home is the stunning kitchen, a culinary haven with numerous upgrades that will delight any chef. From sleek countertops to state-of-the-art appliances, every detail has been meticulously designed. Upstairs you'll find 3 full baths, one of which is a spacious primary bath with an upgraded primary closet. Your Highlands haven awaits!
